{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":604,"text":"Today I want to tell you"},{"time":1820,"text":"about a project being carried out"},{"time":3623,"text":"by scientists all over the world"},{"time":6310,"text":"to paint a neural portrait of the human mind."},{"time":9598,"text":"And the central idea of this work"},{"time":11770,"text":"is that the human mind and brain"},{"time":13628,"text":"is not a single, general-purpose processor,"},{"time":16485,"text":"but a collection of highly specialized components,"},{"time":19927,"text":"each solving a different specific problem,"},{"time":22910,"text":"and yet collectively making up"},{"time":25246,"text":"who we are as human beings and thinkers."},{"time":29602,"text":"To give you a feel for this idea,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":31078,"text":"imagine the following scenario:"},{"time":33742,"text":"You walk into your child's day care center."},{"time":35938,"text":"As usual, there's a dozen kids there"},{"time":38175,"text":"waiting to get picked up,"},{"time":39766,"text":"but this time,"},{"time":41398,"text":"the children's faces look weirdly similar,"},{"time":44383,"text":"and you can't figure out which child is yours."},{"time":47191,"text":"Do you need new glasses?"},{"time":48940,"text":"Are you losing your mind?"},{"time":50848,"text":"You run through a quick mental checklist."},{"time":53300,"text":"No, you seem to be thinking clearly,"},{"time":55194,"text":"and your vision is perfectly sharp."},{"time":57585,"text":"And everything looks normal"},{"time":59374,"text":"except the children's faces."},{"time":61536,"text":"You can see the faces,"},{"time":63322,"text":"but they don't look distinctive,"},{"time":65030,"text":"and none of them looks familiar,"},{"time":66888,"text":"and it's only by spotting an orange hair ribbon"},{"time":69386,"text":"that you find your daughter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":71282,"text":"This sudden loss of the ability to recognize faces"},{"time":74707,"text":"actually happens to people."},{"time":76253,"text":"It's called prosopagnosia,"},{"time":78307,"text":"and it results from damage"},{"time":79488,"text":"to a particular part of the brain."},{"time":81614,"text":"The striking thing about it"},{"time":83114,"text":"is that only face recognition is impaired;"},{"time":85709,"text":"everything else is just fine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":88148,"text":"Prosopagnosia is one of many surprisingly specific"},{"time":92016,"text":"mental deficits that can happen after brain damage."},{"time":96551,"text":"These syndromes collectively"},{"time":97914,"text":"have suggested for a long time"},{"time":100153,"text":"that the mind is divvied up into distinct components,"},{"time":103921,"text":"but the effort to discover those components"},{"time":106306,"text":"has jumped to warp speed"},{"time":107920,"text":"with the invention of brain imaging technology,"},{"time":110502,"text":"especially MRI."},{"time":113550,"text":"So MRI enables you to see internal anatomy"},{"time":116790,"text":"at high resolution,"},{"time":118376,"text":"so I'm going to show you in a second"},{"time":119806,"text":"a set of MRI cross-sectional images"},{"time":123158,"text":"through a familiar object,"},{"time":124776,"text":"and we're going to fly through them"},{"time":125651,"text":"and you're going to try to figure out what the object is."},{"time":128124,"text":"Here we go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":132241,"text":"It's not that easy. It's an artichoke."}]},{"cues":[{"time":134130,"text":"Okay, let's try another one,"},{"time":135760,"text":"starting from the bottom and going through the top."},{"time":140812,"text":"Broccoli! It's a head of broccoli."},{"time":141963,"text":"Isn't it beautiful? I love that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143627,"text":"Okay, here's another one. It's a brain, of course."},{"time":146384,"text":"In fact, it's my brain."},{"time":147970,"text":"We're going through slices through my head like that."},{"time":149703,"text":"That's my nose over on the right, and now"},{"time":151461,"text":"we're going over here, right there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":154870,"text":"So this picture's nice, if I do say so myself,"},{"time":159471,"text":"but it shows only anatomy."},{"time":161383,"text":"The really cool advance with functional imaging"},{"time":163903,"text":"happened when scientists figured out how to make"},{"time":165475,"text":"pictures that show not just anatomy but activity,"},{"time":168870,"text":"that is, where neurons are firing."},{"time":171305,"text":"So here's how this works."},{"time":172821,"text":"Brains are like muscles."},{"time":173938,"text":"When they get active,"},{"time":175501,"text":"they need increased blood flow to supply that activity,"},{"time":178475,"text":"and lucky for us, blood flow\ncontrol to the brain is local,"},{"time":182043,"text":"so if a bunch of neurons, say, right there"},{"time":184205,"text":"get active and start firing,"},{"time":185705,"text":"then blood flow increases just right there."},{"time":188430,"text":"So functional MRI picks up\non that blood flow increase,"},{"time":192151,"text":"producing a higher MRI response"},{"time":194184,"text":"where neural activity goes up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":197110,"text":"So to give you a concrete feel"},{"time":198810,"text":"for how a functional MRI experiment goes"},{"time":201295,"text":"and what you can learn from it"},{"time":202734,"text":"and what you can't,"},{"time":204118,"text":"let me describe one of the first studies I ever did."},{"time":207560,"text":"We wanted to know if there was a special\npart of the brain for recognizing faces,"},{"time":211698,"text":"and there was already reason to\nthink there might be such a thing"},{"time":214770,"text":"based on this phenomenon of prosopagnosia"},{"time":216490,"text":"that I described a moment ago,"},{"time":218613,"text":"but nobody had ever seen that part of the brain"},{"time":220891,"text":"in a normal person,"},{"time":222810,"text":"so we set out to look for it."},{"time":224866,"text":"So I was the first subject."},{"time":226817,"text":"I went into the scanner, I lay on my back,"},{"time":229029,"text":"I held my head as still as I could"},{"time":231612,"text":"while staring at pictures of faces like these"},{"time":236629,"text":"and objects like these"},{"time":238760,"text":"and faces and objects for hours."},{"time":243925,"text":"So as somebody who has\npretty close to the world record"},{"time":246697,"text":"of total number of hours spent inside an MRI scanner,"},{"time":250240,"text":"I can tell you that one of the skills"},{"time":251672,"text":"that's really important for MRI research"},{"time":254335,"text":"is bladder control."},{"time":256113,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":257915,"text":"When I got out of the scanner,"},{"time":259452,"text":"I did a quick analysis of the data,"},{"time":261768,"text":"looking for any parts of my brain"},{"time":263271,"text":"that produced a higher response\nwhen I was looking at faces"},{"time":266077,"text":"than when I was looking at objects,"},{"time":267947,"text":"and here's what I saw."},{"time":270118,"text":"Now this image looks just awful by today's standards,"},{"time":273774,"text":"but at the time I thought it was beautiful."},{"time":276582,"text":"What it shows is that region right there,"},{"time":278532,"text":"that little blob,"},{"time":279815,"text":"it's about the size of an olive"},{"time":281562,"text":"and it's on the bottom surface of my brain"},{"time":283718,"text":"about an inch straight in from right there."},{"time":286924,"text":"And what that part of my brain is doing"},{"time":289714,"text":"is producing a higher MRI response,"},{"time":292634,"text":"that is, higher neural activity,"},{"time":294382,"text":"when I was looking at faces"},{"time":295864,"text":"than when I was looking at objects."},{"time":298130,"text":"So that's pretty cool,"},{"time":299490,"text":"but how do we know this isn't a fluke?"},{"time":301808,"text":"Well, the easiest way"},{"time":303228,"text":"is to just do the experiment again."},{"time":305342,"text":"So I got back in the scanner,"},{"time":306981,"text":"I looked at more faces and I looked at more objects"},{"time":309412,"text":"and I got a similar blob,"},{"time":311601,"text":"and then I did it again"},{"time":313496,"text":"and I did it again"},{"time":315351,"text":"and again and again,"},{"time":318423,"text":"and around about then"},{"time":319470,"text":"I decided to believe it was for real."},{"time":322411,"text":"But still, maybe this is\nsomething weird about my brain"},{"time":326164,"text":"and no one else has one of these things in there,"},{"time":328626,"text":"so to find out, we scanned a bunch of other people"},{"time":331081,"text":"and found that pretty much everyone"},{"time":333527,"text":"has that little face-processing region"},{"time":335533,"text":"in a similar neighborhood of the brain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":338426,"text":"So the next question was,"},{"time":340314,"text":"what does this thing really do?"},{"time":341788,"text":"Is it really specialized just for face recognition?"},{"time":345720,"text":"Well, maybe not, right?"},{"time":346960,"text":"Maybe it responds not only to faces"},{"time":348762,"text":"but to any body part."},{"time":350871,"text":"Maybe it responds to anything human"},{"time":353240,"text":"or anything alive"},{"time":355020,"text":"or anything round."},{"time":356676,"text":"The only way to be really sure that that region"},{"time":358830,"text":"is specialized for face recognition"},{"time":361247,"text":"is to rule out all of those hypotheses."},{"time":363890,"text":"So we spent much of the next couple of years"},{"time":366720,"text":"scanning subjects while they looked at lots"},{"time":368367,"text":"of different kinds of images,"},{"time":369973,"text":"and we showed that that part of the brain"},{"time":371930,"text":"responds strongly when you look at"},{"time":373880,"text":"any images that are faces of any kind,"},{"time":377333,"text":"and it responds much less strongly"},{"time":379246,"text":"to any image you show that isn't a face,"},{"time":382395,"text":"like some of these."}]},{"cues":[{"time":383700,"text":"So have we finally nailed the case"},{"time":385939,"text":"that this region is necessary for face recognition?"},{"time":389179,"text":"No, we haven't."},{"time":390502,"text":"Brain imaging can never tell you"},{"time":392453,"text":"if a region is necessary for anything."},{"time":394893,"text":"All you can do with brain imaging"},{"time":396333,"text":"is watch regions turn on and off"},{"time":398381,"text":"as people think different thoughts."},{"time":400349,"text":"To tell if a part of the brain is\nnecessary for a mental function,"},{"time":403960,"text":"you need to mess with it and see what happens,"},{"time":406469,"text":"and normally we don't get to do that."},{"time":408744,"text":"But an amazing opportunity came about"},{"time":411328,"text":"very recently when a couple of colleagues of mine"},{"time":413792,"text":"tested this man who has epilepsy"},{"time":416863,"text":"and who is shown here in his hospital bed"},{"time":419545,"text":"where he's just had electrodes placed"},{"time":420912,"text":"on the surface of his brain"},{"time":422983,"text":"to identify the source of his seizures."},{"time":425537,"text":"So it turned out by total chance"},{"time":428070,"text":"that two of the electrodes"},{"time":430019,"text":"happened to be right on top of his face area."},{"time":433242,"text":"So with the patient's consent,"},{"time":435571,"text":"the doctors asked him what happened"},{"time":438158,"text":"when they electrically stimulated\nthat part of his brain."},{"time":442324,"text":"Now, the patient doesn't know"},{"time":443978,"text":"where those electrodes are,"},{"time":445362,"text":"and he's never heard of the face area."},{"time":447574,"text":"So let's watch what happens."},{"time":449565,"text":"It's going to start with a control condition"},{"time":451534,"text":"that will say \"Sham\" nearly invisibly"},{"time":453941,"text":"in red in the lower left,"},{"time":455651,"text":"when no current is delivered,"},{"time":457933,"text":"and you'll hear the neurologist speaking\nto the patient first. So let's watch."}]},{"cues":[{"time":461748,"text":"(Video) Neurologist: Okay, just look at my face"},{"time":463829,"text":"and tell me what happens when I do this."},{"time":467114,"text":"All right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":468048,"text":"Patient: Okay."}]},{"cues":[{"time":470871,"text":"Neurologist: One, two, three."}]},{"cues":[{"time":475191,"text":"Patient: Nothing.\nNeurologist: Nothing? Okay."},{"time":478206,"text":"I'm going to do it one more time."},{"time":480613,"text":"Look at my face."},{"time":483807,"text":"One, two, three."}]},{"cues":[{"time":488307,"text":"Patient: You just turned into somebody else."},{"time":491131,"text":"Your face metamorphosed."},{"time":493268,"text":"Your nose got saggy, it went to the left."},{"time":496279,"text":"You almost looked like somebody I'd seen before,"},{"time":499815,"text":"but somebody different."},{"time":502449,"text":"That was a trip."},{"time":504521,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":507653,"text":"Nancy Kanwisher: So this experiment —"},{"time":509268,"text":"(Applause) —"},{"time":513491,"text":"this experiment finally nails the case"},{"time":516173,"text":"that this region of the brain is not only"},{"time":517998,"text":"selectively responsive to faces"},{"time":520135,"text":"but causally involved in face perception."},{"time":523180,"text":"So I went through all of these details"},{"time":525310,"text":"about the face region to show you what it takes"},{"time":527774,"text":"to really establish that a part of the brain"},{"time":530113,"text":"is selectively involved in a specific mental process."},{"time":533241,"text":"Next, I'll go through much more quickly"},{"time":535400,"text":"some of the other specialized regions of the brain"},{"time":538060,"text":"that we and others have found."},{"time":540160,"text":"So to do this, I've spent a lot of time"},{"time":542274,"text":"in the scanner over the last month"},{"time":544141,"text":"so I can show you these things in my brain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":546402,"text":"So let's get started. Here's my right hemisphere."},{"time":549635,"text":"So we're oriented like that.\nYou're looking at my head this way."},{"time":552297,"text":"Imagine taking the skull off"},{"time":553390,"text":"and looking at the surface of the brain like that."},{"time":555658,"text":"Okay, now as you can see,"},{"time":557416,"text":"the surface of the brain is all folded up."},{"time":558919,"text":"So that's not good. Stuff could be hidden in there."},{"time":560640,"text":"We want to see the whole thing,"},{"time":562074,"text":"so let's inflate it so we can see the whole thing."},{"time":565386,"text":"Next, let's find that face area I've been talking about"},{"time":568215,"text":"that responds to images like these."},{"time":570442,"text":"To see that, let's turn the brain around"},{"time":571961,"text":"and look on the inside surface on the bottom,"},{"time":573980,"text":"and there it is, that's my face area."},{"time":576285,"text":"Just to the right of that is another region"},{"time":578992,"text":"that is shown in purple"},{"time":580630,"text":"that responds when you process color information,"},{"time":583702,"text":"and near those regions are other regions"},{"time":586393,"text":"that are involved in perceiving places,"},{"time":588756,"text":"like right now, I'm seeing\nthis layout of space around me"},{"time":591594,"text":"and these regions in green right there"},{"time":593346,"text":"are really active."},{"time":594620,"text":"There's another one out on the outside surface again"},{"time":596990,"text":"where there's a couple more face regions as well."},{"time":599795,"text":"Also in this vicinity"},{"time":602140,"text":"is a region that's selectively involved"},{"time":603785,"text":"in processing visual motion,"},{"time":605721,"text":"like these moving dots here,"},{"time":607225,"text":"and that's in yellow at the bottom of the brain,"},{"time":609914,"text":"and near that is a region that responds"},{"time":613082,"text":"when you look at images of bodies and body parts"},{"time":615979,"text":"like these, and that region is shown in lime green"},{"time":618724,"text":"at the bottom of the brain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":620727,"text":"Now all these regions I've shown you so far"},{"time":623359,"text":"are involved in specific aspects of visual perception."},{"time":627791,"text":"Do we also have specialized brain regions"},{"time":629939,"text":"for other senses, like hearing?"},{"time":632752,"text":"Yes, we do. So if we turn the brain around a little bit,"},{"time":635789,"text":"here's a region in dark blue"},{"time":638190,"text":"that we reported just a couple of months ago,"},{"time":640536,"text":"and this region responds strongly"},{"time":642170,"text":"when you hear sounds with pitch, like these."},{"time":645599,"text":"(Sirens)"},{"time":647742,"text":"(Cello music)"},{"time":649823,"text":"(Doorbell)"},{"time":651740,"text":"In contrast, that same region\ndoes not respond strongly"},{"time":655348,"text":"when you hear perfectly familiar sounds"},{"time":656910,"text":"that don't have a clear pitch, like these."},{"time":659272,"text":"(Chomping)"},{"time":661741,"text":"(Drum roll)"},{"time":663941,"text":"(Toilet flushing)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":666708,"text":"Okay. Next to the pitch region"},{"time":669206,"text":"is another set of regions that\nare selectively responsive"},{"time":671680,"text":"when you hear the sounds of speech."}]},{"cues":[{"time":674445,"text":"Okay, now let's look at these same regions."},{"time":676285,"text":"In my left hemisphere, there's a similar arrangement —"},{"time":678753,"text":"not identical, but similar —"},{"time":680226,"text":"and most of the same regions are in here,"},{"time":682435,"text":"albeit sometimes different in size."}]},{"cues":[{"time":684437,"text":"Now, everything I've shown you so far"},{"time":686451,"text":"are regions that are involved in\ndifferent aspects of perception,"},{"time":689477,"text":"vision and hearing."},{"time":691310,"text":"Do we also have specialized brain regions"},{"time":692970,"text":"for really fancy, complicated mental processes?"},{"time":696405,"text":"Yes, we do."},{"time":697834,"text":"So here in pink are my language regions."},{"time":701223,"text":"So it's been known for a very long time"},{"time":702651,"text":"that that general vicinity of the brain"},{"time":704686,"text":"is involved in processing language,"},{"time":706879,"text":"but we showed very recently"},{"time":708611,"text":"that these pink regions"},{"time":710321,"text":"respond extremely selectively."},{"time":712526,"text":"They respond when you understand\nthe meaning of a sentence,"},{"time":715338,"text":"but not when you do other complex mental things,"},{"time":718176,"text":"like mental arithmetic"},{"time":720355,"text":"or holding information in memory"},{"time":722751,"text":"or appreciating the complex structure"},{"time":725406,"text":"in a piece of music."}]},{"cues":[{"time":729664,"text":"The most amazing region that's been found yet"},{"time":732553,"text":"is this one right here in turquoise."},{"time":735860,"text":"This region responds"},{"time":738050,"text":"when you think about what another person is thinking."},{"time":742318,"text":"So that may seem crazy,"},{"time":743962,"text":"but actually, we humans do this all the time."},{"time":747830,"text":"You're doing this when you realize"},{"time":750023,"text":"that your partner is going to be worried"},{"time":751654,"text":"if you don't call home to say you're running late."},{"time":754161,"text":"I'm doing this with that region of my brain right now"},{"time":757630,"text":"when I realize that you guys"},{"time":759911,"text":"are probably now wondering about"},{"time":761509,"text":"all that gray, uncharted territory in the brain,"},{"time":764056,"text":"and what's up with that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":766020,"text":"Well, I'm wondering about that too,"},{"time":767705,"text":"and we're running a bunch of\nexperiments in my lab right now"},{"time":770100,"text":"to try to find a number of other"},{"time":772113,"text":"possible specializations in the brain"},{"time":774145,"text":"for other very specific mental functions."},{"time":777513,"text":"But importantly, I don't think we have"},{"time":780134,"text":"specializations in the brain"},{"time":781698,"text":"for every important mental function,"},{"time":784444,"text":"even mental functions that may be critical for survival."},{"time":787853,"text":"In fact, a few years ago,"},{"time":789955,"text":"there was a scientist in my lab"},{"time":791072,"text":"who became quite convinced"},{"time":792481,"text":"that he'd found a brain region"},{"time":794230,"text":"for detecting food,"},{"time":796142,"text":"and it responded really strongly in the scanner"},{"time":798060,"text":"when people looked at images like this."},{"time":800788,"text":"And further, he found a similar response"},{"time":803700,"text":"in more or less the same location"},{"time":805639,"text":"in 10 out of 12 subjects."},{"time":807640,"text":"So he was pretty stoked,"},{"time":809934,"text":"and he was running around the lab"},{"time":811194,"text":"telling everyone that he was going to go on \"Oprah\""},{"time":813196,"text":"with his big discovery."},{"time":815214,"text":"But then he devised the critical test:"},{"time":818236,"text":"He showed subjects images of food like this"},{"time":821419,"text":"and compared them to images with very similar"},{"time":824160,"text":"color and shape, but that weren't food, like these."},{"time":827970,"text":"And his region responded the same"},{"time":830101,"text":"to both sets of images."},{"time":832050,"text":"So it wasn't a food area,"},{"time":833377,"text":"it was just a region that liked colors and shapes."},{"time":836148,"text":"So much for \"Oprah.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":840483,"text":"But then the question, of course, is,"},{"time":842708,"text":"how do we process all this other stuff"},{"time":844834,"text":"that we don't have specialized brain regions for?"},{"time":847804,"text":"Well, I think the answer is that in addition"},{"time":849615,"text":"to these highly specialized components\nthat I've been describing,"},{"time":853169,"text":"we also have a lot of very general-\npurpose machinery in our heads"},{"time":856848,"text":"that enables us to tackle"},{"time":858342,"text":"whatever problem comes along."},{"time":860448,"text":"In fact, we've shown recently that"},{"time":862503,"text":"these regions here in white"},{"time":864571,"text":"respond whenever you do any difficult mental task"},{"time":867982,"text":"at all —"},{"time":869083,"text":"well, of the seven that we've tested."},{"time":872654,"text":"So each of the brain regions that I've described"},{"time":874823,"text":"to you today"},{"time":876129,"text":"is present in approximately the same location"},{"time":878896,"text":"in every normal subject."},{"time":880638,"text":"I could take any of you,"},{"time":882261,"text":"pop you in the scanner,"},{"time":883487,"text":"and find each of those regions in your brain,"},{"time":885772,"text":"and it would look a lot like my brain,"},{"time":887677,"text":"although the regions would be slightly different"},{"time":889747,"text":"in their exact location and in their size."}]},{"cues":[{"time":893311,"text":"What's important to me about this work"},{"time":895676,"text":"is not the particular locations of these brain regions,"},{"time":898645,"text":"but the simple fact that we have"},{"time":901232,"text":"selective, specific components of mind and brain"},{"time":903800,"text":"in the first place."},{"time":905448,"text":"I mean, it could have been otherwise."},{"time":907459,"text":"The brain could have been a single,"},{"time":909900,"text":"general-purpose processor,"},{"time":911395,"text":"more like a kitchen knife"},{"time":912867,"text":"than a Swiss Army knife."},{"time":914550,"text":"Instead, what brain imaging has delivered"},{"time":917661,"text":"is this rich and interesting picture of the human mind."},{"time":921507,"text":"So we have this picture of very general-purpose"},{"time":923970,"text":"machinery in our heads"},{"time":925040,"text":"in addition to this surprising array"},{"time":927397,"text":"of very specialized components."}]},{"cues":[{"time":931712,"text":"It's early days in this enterprise."},{"time":933865,"text":"We've painted only the first brushstrokes"},{"time":936641,"text":"in our neural portrait of the human mind."},{"time":939568,"text":"The most fundamental questions remain unanswered."},{"time":942650,"text":"So for example, what does each\nof these regions do exactly?"},{"time":946450,"text":"Why do we need three face areas"},{"time":948592,"text":"and three place areas,"},{"time":950057,"text":"and what's the division of labor between them?"},{"time":952925,"text":"Second, how are all these things"},{"time":955618,"text":"connected in the brain?"},{"time":957330,"text":"With diffusion imaging,"},{"time":958917,"text":"you can trace bundles of neurons"},{"time":961096,"text":"that connect to different parts of the brain,"},{"time":963671,"text":"and with this method shown here,"},{"time":965302,"text":"you can trace the connections of\nindividual neurons in the brain,"},{"time":968999,"text":"potentially someday giving us a wiring diagram"},{"time":971717,"text":"of the entire human brain."},{"time":973783,"text":"Third, how does all of this"},{"time":975830,"text":"very systematic structure get built,"},{"time":978979,"text":"both over development in childhood"},{"time":981935,"text":"and over the evolution of our species?"},{"time":984747,"text":"To address questions like that,"},{"time":986647,"text":"scientists are now scanning"},{"time":988430,"text":"other species of animals,"},{"time":990587,"text":"and they're also scanning human infants."}]},{"cues":[{"time":996931,"text":"Many people justify the high\ncost of neuroscience research"},{"time":1000582,"text":"by pointing out that it may help us someday"},{"time":1003336,"text":"to treat brain disorders like Alzheimer's and autism."},{"time":1006793,"text":"That's a hugely important goal,"},{"time":1008740,"text":"and I'd be thrilled if any of my work contributed to it,"},{"time":1011961,"text":"but fixing things that are broken in the world"},{"time":1014959,"text":"is not the only thing that's worth doing."},{"time":1017760,"text":"The effort to understand the human mind and brain"},{"time":1020988,"text":"is worthwhile even if it never led to the treatment"},{"time":1023806,"text":"of a single disease."},{"time":1025483,"text":"What could be more thrilling"},{"time":1027520,"text":"than to understand the fundamental mechanisms"},{"time":1030661,"text":"that underlie human experience,"},{"time":1032957,"text":"to understand, in essence, who we are?"},{"time":1035883,"text":"This is, I think, the greatest scientific quest"},{"time":1039332,"text":"of all time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1042045,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}